  • Changelog

    Cleaned self-paced reading data of Frank, Fernandez Monsalve, Thompson et al. (2013)

    data_frank2013_spr.Rd

    A cleaned version of dataset "data_frank2013_spr_complete": No sentences with typos, only native speakers, and subjects with accuracy over 0.8 from Frank, Fernandez Monsalve, Thompson et al. (2013)

    Usage

    data_frank2013_spr

    Format

    An object of class tidytable (inherits from data.table, data.frame) with 165040 rows and 12 columns.

    References

    1 S. L. Frank, I. Fernandez Monsalve, R. L. Thompson, et al. ``Reading Time Data for Evaluating Broad-Coverage Models of English Sentence Processing''. In: Behavior Research Methods 45.4 (dec. 01, 2013), pp. 1182--1190. ISSN: 1554-3528. DOI: 10.3758/s13428-012-0313-y.

    See also

    data_frank2013_stimuli for the enriched stimuli, data_frank2013_spr_complete for the complete version of this dataset, data_frank2013_et_fix for the eye-tracking version of this dataset with the fixation information, and data_frank2013_et_rt for a preprocessed eye-tracking dataset.

    Other datasets: data_frank2013_et_rt, data_frank2013_spr_complete, data_frank2013_stimuli, data_provo_cloze
